summary: The PromptBase marketplace is mature and highly specialized in visual content, dominated by Midjourney prompts, with strong engagement in the $3-$5 price range. Key growth areas include high-concept art styles (Surreal, Retro, Fantasy) and emerging video generation models (Veo, Sora). The platform is actively pushing professional creator tools (PromptBase Pro) and enterprise services (Hire AI Creator) beyond simple prompt purchasing.
